od and Katie Spencer\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.eonline.com/news/898406/critics-choice-awards-2018-complete-list-of-movie-and-tv-nominations |title=Critics' Choice Awards 2018: Complete List of Movie and TV Nominations |last=Johnson |first=Zach |work=E! |date=December 6, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Costume Design|Best Costume Design]]\n| Jacqueline Durran\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Makeup|Best Hair & Makeup]]\n| ''Beauty and the Beast''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Song|Best Song]]\n| \"Evermore\"\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[23rd Empire Awards|Empire Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"| March 18, 2018\n| [[Empire Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| [[Emma Watson]]\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/empire-film-awards-2018-the-last-jedi-leads-the-pack-with-nine-nominations-including-best-film-a3744171.html |title=Empire Film Awards 2018: The Last Jedi leads the pack with nine nominations including Best Actress for Daisy Ridley |first=Jennifer |last=Ruby |newspaper=[[London Evening Standard]] |date=January 19, 2018 |accessdate=January 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180130152451/https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/empire-film-awards-2018-the-last-jedi-leads-the-pack-with-nine-nominations-including-best-film-a3744171.html |archive-date=January 30, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref><br /><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-last-jedi-leads-nominations-uks-empire-awards-1076867 |title='Star Wars: The Last Jedi' Leads Nominations for U.K.'s Empire Awards |first=Alex |last=Ritman |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=January 22, 2018 |accessdate=January 29, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116051210/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/star-wars-last-jedi-leads-no