ading-feature-film-1058855|title=HPA Awards: 'Dunkirk' Wins Best Editing in a Feature|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=November 18, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201044546/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/hollywood-professional-association-awards-winners-2017-list-full-1058842/item/outstanding-color-grading-feature-film-1058855|archivedate=December 1, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Outstanding Visual Effects \u2013 Feature Film\n| Kyle McCulloch, Glen Pratt, Richard Hoover, Dale Newton, Neil Weatherley and [[Framestore]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Houston Film Critics Society Awards 2017|Houston Film Critics Society]]\n| January 6, 2018\n| Best Original Song\n| \"Evermore\" \u2013 Alan Menken and Tim Rice\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.houstonchronicle.com/entertainment/movies/article/The-Shape-of-Water-inundates-Houston-critics-12423977.php|title='The Shape of Water' inundates Houston critics' film awards nominations|date=December 12, 2017|newspaper=[[Houston Chronicle]]|accessdate=December 12, 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213081831/http://www.houstonchronicle.com/entertainment/movies/article/The-Shape-of-Water-inundates-Houston-critics-12423977.php|archivedate=December 13, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Make-Up Artists and Hair Stylists Guild]]\n| February 24, 2018\n| Feature Motion Picture: Best Period and/or Character Hair\n| Jenny Shircore, Marc Pilcher and Charlotte Hayward\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2018-makeup-artists-hair-stylists-guild-award-nominations-1067879/item/feature-motion-picture-best-contemporary-makeup-1067899 |title=Makeup Artists and Hair Stylists Guild Awards: 'Darkest Hour,' 'Wonder' Lead Feature Nominees |first=Carolyn |last=Giardina |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=January 5, 2018 |accessdate=January 5, 2018 |archive-url=htt